nally, we briefly discuss the\ndetectability of metal-free stellar clusters with the James Webb Space\nTelescope.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 17 May 2012 01:12:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Aug 2012 19:32:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-02-28"}
